{"tid":2265251,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"深入淺出–殺蟲劑會否對益蟲造成不良影響？","createTime":"2020-10-31T09:36:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-02T12:44:44.000Z","uid":38861,"like":23,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8694ba8d29fce51e652e39cc8f80abe0eee8bc25","tid":2265251,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T09:36:27.000Z","msg":"全球約有35%的食物產量，均依靠傳粉者例如蜜蜂等支撐而成。而甲蟲、蟻蛉等昆蟲則幫忙捕食蛀食農作物的害蟲，讓農作物得以健康成長。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2VUqxZj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2VUqxZj.jpg&h=6ed4ceb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在這個層上，農作物所使用的化學殺蟲劑，究竟會否對益蟲造成傷害?<br />\n<br />\n(圖2)Neonicotinoid insecticides為舊式殺蟲劑的一種，內含的Neonicotinoid物質會與昆蟲神經線內的NAChRs結合，引致昆蟲的神經系統癱瘓而致死。<br />\n<br />\n想知更多關於裡頭的相關機制，可參閱:<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/article/477009\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Farticle%2F477009&d=DHxvyfXarR7adKHN0UsakwNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=0abf72ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/article/477009</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dhvJjEn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdhvJjEn.jpg&h=fc0eb8de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n因著其擁有對昆蟲無差別的攻擊特性，益蟲害蟲均會送命。<br />\n正因如此，全球均已有措施禁用此類殺蟲劑，以歐盟EU地區最為嚴厲。<br />\n<br />\n題外話，人類與昆蟲的NAChRs有著結構式的分別，所以殺蟲劑對人類的傷害相對上較細。<br />\n<br />\n(圖3)基於舊式殺蟲劑的禁用，新式殺蟲劑已開始廣泛使用。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ep1DSZr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fep1DSZr.jpg&h=55035950&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nButanolide and sulfoximine-based insecticides為兩款新式的殺蟲劑，但其殺害昆蟲的原理跟舊式一模一樣。<br />\n<br />\n新式與舊式重大的分別在於其化學結構的不同，根據IRAC(Insecticide Resistance Action Committee)的分類方式，舊式殺蟲劑界定為4A組別，而新式殺蟲劑界定為4C及4D組別。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(圖4)那麼新式殺蟲劑除化學分類組別的不同之外，對比舊式殺蟲劑還有甚麼過人之處呢?<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UtbsMju.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUtbsMju.jpg&h=694bd981&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n答案是接近沒有過人之處，它們對益蟲依舊造成傷害。<br />\n<br />\nFlupyradifurone的穩定性與舊式殺蟲劑接近一樣，能長年積累在環境裡頭。<br />\n<br />\n以蜜蜂為例，雖然低劑量不會對東方蜜蜂(<em>Apis cerana</em>)造成重大修亡，但同等劑量會引致西方蜜蜂(<em>A. mellifera</em>)大量死亡。<br />\n<br />\n相對上，另一款新式殺蟲劑Sulfoxaflor的穩定性則有所減低，2-3日後在大自然的濃度會減退50%。<br />\n奈何它對蜜蜂生育率造成顯著的不良影響，歐洲熊蜂(<em>B. terrestris</em>)在低劑量的影響下，生蛋率及幼蟲孵化率分別下降31及40%。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n顯然，新式化學殺蟲劑並沒有改善舊式殺蟲劑的問題。<br />\n<br />\n在審核殺蟲劑安全性的時候，往往只會對數款昆蟲作出毒性的檢驗，但大自然的昆蟲品種何其之多，加上昆蟲本身的獨特性，對一款益蟲無害並不等於對另一款無害，因此難以評估真實對大自然的影響。<br />\n<br />\n同時間，現有的評核制度並沒有估核對昆蟲往後的生育影響，這將是一道值得深思應否加進評核殺蟲劑安全性的條件之一。<br />\n<br />\n以上的資料來源均取自Ref1。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去<span class=\"blue\">Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單</span>俾一個<span class=\"green\">like</span>以及<span class=\"red\">Bookmark</span>，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=DHxvyfXarR7adKHN0UsakwNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=c4360f3d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「<span class=\"gold\">買一嚿/半嚿薯仔</span>」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=DHxvyfXarR7adKHN0UsakwNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=80324e44\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有興趣接收科學資訊的話，歡迎follow IG: potatopigtongue。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/potatopigtongue/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fpotatopigtongue%2F&d=DHxvyfXarR7adKHN0UsakwNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=6279006a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/potatopigtongue/</a><br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC7542824/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC7542824%2F&d=DHxvyfXarR7adKHN0UsakwNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=46aa54a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC7542824/</a>"},{"pid":"dd7e04c3a77fb40695353dac072ab5da31c5a210","tid":2265251,"uid":29929,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T09:37:30.000Z","msg":"成撚日唔覆我 on99"},{"pid":"0ada6f5782cbde1ec43793b014ba996d4be32787","tid":2265251,"uid":237487,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T09:40:24.000Z","msg":"巴打有冇啲關於竉物嘅資訊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8aa3d2cd23a6a1d7dff8e8db90d64f2d908679f","tid":2265251,"uid":199689,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T09:41:50.000Z","msg":"點解會依個時間出文<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/what.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cb8c9f6826b20386c9b23b87ae0ac508690cbd0","tid":2265251,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0ada6f5782cbde1ec43793b014ba996d4be32787","tid":2265251,"uid":237487,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T09:40:24.000Z","msg":"巴打有冇啲關於竉物嘅資訊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T09:42:33.000Z","msg":"深入淺出&ndash;貓隻會否因為捕捉老鼠而患上鼠疫<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2219394\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2219394</a><br />\n<br />\n唔知依個算唔算<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78940f7dc05